  "detailed_description": "<h1>Early Access Info and Languages</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Since launching in Early Access in July 2024, Ova Magica has gotten three major content updates, plenty of patches, and is now heading toward its full 1.0 release. <br><br>Save files are fully supported across all Early Access updates and into 1.0, so you keep all  your progress.<br><br>Ova Magica currently only supports <strong>English</strong>. The 1.0 comes with other languages, which include German, Spanish, French, Japanese, and Simplified Chinese.  </p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ova Magica combines the best of the JRPG, farming, and monster taming genres with life-sim elements - to bring you a content-rich game inspired by the classics!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLOBS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and train cute blob creatures. Ova Magica features an extensive crossbreeding system that allows you to create your very own unique blob  from millions of combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=640 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.mp4?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many blobs can help you with everyday tasks or give you the upper hand in battles. A turtle blob is your best friend for watering crops, a cow blob produces milk and a bat blob helps you with bug catching. Collect all blobs to discover their unique abilities!    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FRIENDSHIP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/e8a3c898485cc1ebbcbf51568d26965d.avif?t=1765294922\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras_big/e8a3c898485cc1ebbcbf51568d26965d.avif?t=1765294922 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend 13 different characters, each with a unique story and personality! Deepen your relationship to unlock special events, items and buildings and help make Clover Town a better place!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FARMING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow several plants and trees! Sell the harvest, feed your blobs with it or use it to cook even better food! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/55e7eacdfe2414848ae43be9d3d2b632.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=620 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/55e7eacdfe2414848ae43be9d3d2b632.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEASONS + FESTIVALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play trough the main three seasons which all come with unique festivals, activities, blobs and crops!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/f9d18a37142e69f964bff788601dcf94.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=670 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/f9d18a37142e69f964bff788601dcf94.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPEDITION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on adventure into the blob worlds to find rare treasure and blob eggs. But be careful! The worlds change every time you enter and are roamed by wild blobs. With great risk comes great reward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=782 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.mp4?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFTING </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources to craft new useful blueprints with the workbench or decorate your farm and home!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/405f98957de21acbc86f658d01551826.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=620 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/405f98957de21acbc86f658d01551826.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ova Magica has many more features that you can gradually discover as you progress through the game!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ova Magica combines the best of the JRPG, farming, and monster taming genres with life-sim elements - to bring you a content-rich game inspired by the classics!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BLOBS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and train cute blob creatures. Ova Magica features an extensive crossbreeding system that allows you to create your very own unique blob  from millions of combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=640 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/950676b45de762c4759a95cb3ec11664.mp4?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many blobs can help you with everyday tasks or give you the upper hand in battles. A turtle blob is your best friend for watering crops, a cow blob produces milk and a bat blob helps you with bug catching. Collect all blobs to discover their unique abilities!    </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FRIENDSHIP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/e8a3c898485cc1ebbcbf51568d26965d.avif?t=1765294922\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras_big/e8a3c898485cc1ebbcbf51568d26965d.avif?t=1765294922 width=800 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Befriend 13 different characters, each with a unique story and personality! Deepen your relationship to unlock special events, items and buildings and help make Clover Town a better place!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FARMING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow several plants and trees! Sell the harvest, feed your blobs with it or use it to cook even better food! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/55e7eacdfe2414848ae43be9d3d2b632.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=620 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/55e7eacdfe2414848ae43be9d3d2b632.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEASONS + FESTIVALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play trough the main three seasons which all come with unique festivals, activities, blobs and crops!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/f9d18a37142e69f964bff788601dcf94.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=670 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/f9d18a37142e69f964bff788601dcf94.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPEDITION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go on adventure into the blob worlds to find rare treasure and blob eggs. But be careful! The worlds change every time you enter and are roamed by wild blobs. With great risk comes great reward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=782 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/5bb19894c472a6404ac941cbd18c3296.mp4?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFTING </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather resources to craft new useful blueprints with the workbench or decorate your farm and home!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/405f98957de21acbc86f658d01551826.poster.avif?t=1765294922\" width=620 height=305 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1299170/extras/405f98957de21acbc86f658d01551826.webm?t=1765294922\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ova Magica has many more features that you can gradually discover as you progress through the game!</p>",
